# TLS certificates and private keys -- never commit these. A dev
# self-signed cert (certs/key.pem) was committed once historically
# (commit 8dfa1c6) and later removed (8ce3e0c), but nothing structurally
# prevented it from happening again. Certs are meant to be generated
# locally / by CI (see .github/workflows/tests.yml, docker-compose.yml)
# or supplied via a secrets manager in production -- never checked in.
certs/
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
